Package mosais.distribution

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    TreeNodeModel
    This is an interface for quadtrees to communicate with the concept they're modelling without needing to know what exactly they are modelling.

    Class Description
    BestCandidatePlot
    A distribution that uses the best candidate algorithm to make sure points are uniformly distributed.
    BoundingBox

    BoundingBoxTest  
    PlotTree
    A quadtree backed distribution of points in a two dimensional plane.

    Quadtree<E>

    RandomPlot
